  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that mathematical algorithm can identify freezing episodes
      based on data obtained from accelerometer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The subjects will walk with an accelerometer. The acceleration traces will be online
      analyzed, and if freezing episode is recognized, an auditory cue will be heard.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
